name: css-ease
readme:
# css-ease

  css easing functions, taken from [visionmedia/move.js](/visionmedia/move.js).

## Installation

  Install with [component(1)](http://component.io):

    $ component install yields/css-ease

  or via [npm](https://www.npmjs.com):

    $ npm install css-ease

## Example

```js
ease.snap; // => "cubic-bezier(0,1,.5,1)"
```
